+------------------+----------------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+------------------------------+
| Scope            | Descrizione                                        | Servlet (Java)                                | JSP (Scriptlet)                                         | EL (Expression Language)    | JavaScript (client-side)    |
+------------------+----------------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+------------------------------+
| page             | Visibile solo nella pagina JSP corrente            | ✖                                             | pageContext.getAttribute("name")                        | ${pageScope.name}           | ✖                            |
|                  |                                                    |                                               | pageContext.setAttribute("name", value)                 |                             |                              |
+------------------+----------------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+------------------------------+
| request          | Valida per tutte le risorse nella stessa richiesta | request.getAttribute("name")                  | request.getAttribute("name")                            | ${requestScope.name}        | ✖                            |
|                  |                                                    | request.setAttribute("name", value)           | request.setAttribute("name", value)                     |                             |                              |
+------------------+----------------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+------------------------------+
| session          | Valida per tutte le richieste dello stesso client  | request.getSession().getAttribute("name")     | session.getAttribute("name")                            | ${sessionScope.name}        | sessionStorage.getItem("n") |
|                  |                                                    | request.getSession().setAttribute("name", v)  | session.setAttribute("name", value)                     |                             | sessionStorage.setItem("n") |
+------------------+----------------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+------------------------------+
| application      | Condivisa tra tutti gli utenti                     | getServletContext().getAttribute("name")      | application.getAttribute("name")                        | ${applicationScope.name}    | localStorage.getItem("n")   |
|                  |                                                    | getServletContext().setAttribute("name", v)   | application.setAttribute("name", value)                 |                             | localStorage.setItem("n")   |
+------------------+----------------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+------------------------------+
| cookie           | Dati persistenti nel browser                       | request.getCookies() / response.addCookie()   | ✖                                                       | ${cookie.name}              | document.cookie             |
+------------------+----------------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+------------------------------+
| hidden field     | Input HTML nascosto (tra richieste HTTP)           | request.getParameter("fieldname")             | request.getParameter("fieldname")                       | ✖                           | <input type="hidden">       |
+------------------+----------------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+------------------------------+


+----------------+---------------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------+
| Funzione       | getParameter()                              | getAttribute()                              |
+----------------+---------------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------+
| Fonte dati     | HTTP request (form, query string)           | Oggetto creato nel codice                   |
+----------------+---------------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------+
| Ritorna        | Solo String                                 | Oggetto Object (cast necessario)            |
+----------------+---------------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------+
| Usi tipici     | Lettura input utente                        | Passaggio di oggetti tra componenti         |
+----------------+---------------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------+
| Modificabile   | ❌ No                                       | ✅ Sì (con setAttribute)                     |
+----------------+---------------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------+
